2235
02:06:42.344 --> 02:06:43.721
[soft laugh]

2236
02:06:43.762 --> 02:06:47.141
♪ I'll put the weight on you ♪

2237
02:06:48.058 --> 02:06:54.773
♪ And I'll do the same thing
That you do ♪

2238
02:06:55.858 --> 02:07:01.280
♪ I'll put the weight on you ♪

2239
