2253
02:08:33.205 --> 02:08:37.209
There are spirits that can do
great physical harm to people.

2254
02:08:37.251 --> 02:08:38.460
[real Ed] In the name
of Jesus Christ

2255
02:08:38.502 --> 02:08:39.461
